data.description: Pristine 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath Craftsman style home on wooded lot in desirable Founders Pointe boasting an open floor plan and quality details inside & out. Great room features an 11' ceiling & gas fireplace. Spacious kitchen features an 8ft Quartz island, gas range, butlers pantry, walk in pantry and eat-in area. Downstairs bedroom/study includes a full bath.  A mudroom, half bath and large dining room complete the downstairs. Hardwood floors, upgraded Mohawk carpeting/padding in bedrooms, plantation shutters & 2" blinds throughout. Spacious primary suite with tray ceiling, huge walk-in closet & bath with soaking tub & separate shower. Two oversized bedrooms with walk-in closets share a jack-n-jill bath. Sizable Media room can be 5th bedrooom. Exquisite outdoor living area includes a wooded backyard that extends beyond fenced yard, large screened porch, custom paver patio with build-in wood burning fireplace, accent lighting & irrigation system. Oversized garage has epoxy flooring.
